00:15:35,541 --> 00:15:38,666
I've made sure
to keep her alive.

253
00:15:39,541 --> 00:15:41,000
If you find yourself
thirsting for blood,

254
00:15:41,083 --> 00:15:43,375
then please, summon me.

255
00:15:43,458 --> 00:15:45,333
After all. That's one
of the reasons why

256
00:15:45,416 --> 00:15:47,625
I'm here to serve
you, Lord Zelman.

257
00:15:48,375 --> 00:15:50,750
You dare to reprimand me?

258
00:15:50,833 --> 00:15:53,125
You've grown
annoying as of late.

259
00:15:53,916 --> 00:15:55,833
So...

260
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:59,333
What is it you've come
to report to me, Sayuka?

261
00:15:59,416 --> 00:16:02,125
Well... The executives
of the Company have

