00:16:10,375 --> 00:16:12,916
He was a member of
the Hong Kong group.

266
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,375
Isn't that right?

267
00:16:14,458 --> 00:16:15,416
Yes, sir.

268
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:16,625
And I believe
he fought alongside

269
00:16:16,708 --> 00:16:18,500
Silver Blade in the crusade.

270
00:16:18,583 --> 00:16:20,875
So he'll be on the
Company's side for sure.

271
00:16:20,958 --> 00:16:22,750
No. He appeared
at the Marine Bank

272
00:16:22,833 --> 00:16:25,291
earlier today to
seek a residence.

273
00:16:25,375 --> 00:16:27,833
Oh-ho. The Warlock house, is it?

274
00:16:27,916 --> 00:16:29,833
But it appears that
Cain Warlock refused to

275
00:16:29,916 --> 00:16:32,041
see him for some
reason or another.

276
00:16:32,125 --> 00:16:35,250
And now, the Silver Blade is
headed towards the Old Yard.

277
00:16:35,333 --> 00:16:37,500
Given this information,
most likely,

278
00:16:37,583 --> 00:16:39,500
he is now on his
way to meet with Sei.

279
00:16:39,583 --> 00:16:42,458
That's great. This
is getting interesting.

280
00:16:42,541 --> 00:16:44,958
However, Auguste Wyker's
group is beginning to show signs

281
00:16:45,041 --> 00:16:47,000
of movement. And I'm
afraid that you will be

282
00:16:47,083 --> 00:16:48,916
held responsible
if they run amuck.

283
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,083
I don't care
about that. Ignore them.

284
00:16:51,166 --> 00:16:51,708
But sir--

285
00:16:51,791 --> 00:16:53,875
I'm over it.

286
00:16:53,958 --> 00:16:56,500
Does The Silver Blade have
a companion traveling with him?

287
00:16:56,583 --> 00:16:59,791
Yes, his younger
brother, supposedly.

288
00:17:00,500 --> 00:17:02,166
I see.

289
00:17:02,791 --> 00:17:04,750
Then who's this I sense?

290
00:17:06,041 --> 00:17:10,000
Has Sei grown so weak
that he hasn't even noticed?

291
00:17:10,083 --> 00:17:12,375
Talk about pathetic.

292
00:17:12,458 --> 00:17:14,333
Pardon me, sir?

293
00:17:19,833 --> 00:17:23,291
Your report
is much appreciated.

294
00:17:24,291 --> 00:17:27,666
It was... nothing.

295
00:17:28,958 --> 00:17:30,625
I'm going out.

296
00:17:30,708 --> 00:17:33,500
But the sun hasn't
set yet. You can't go out.

297
00:17:33,583 --> 00:17:36,000
A VIP who's maintained
his silence for

298
00:17:36,083 --> 00:17:38,583
ten years has come to town.

299
00:17:40,208 --> 00:17:42,750
There's no way I'm
gonna miss his appearance.

300
00:17:44,625 --> 00:17:47,666
Please, Lord Zelman, wait!

301
00:17:59,416 --> 00:18:00,750
Quite impressive.

302
00:18:00,833 --> 00:18:03,208
This is amazing. I can't
believe you can buy things here!

303
00:18:03,291 --> 00:18:04,833
Wow, they sell pots,
clothing, food...

304
00:18:04,916 --> 00:18:07,958
You can find anything!
I wanna live here, brother.

305
00:18:08,041 --> 00:18:09,541
Um, Mimiko.

306
00:18:09,625 --> 00:18:11,541
I just don't
understand why they had to

307
