368
00:21:06,041 --> 00:21:07,833
Well, you may be safe today,

369
00:21:07,916 --> 00:21:10,500
but you never know
what might happen tomorrow.

370
00:21:10,583 --> 00:21:12,083
Is that supposed to be a threat?

371
00:21:12,166 --> 00:21:15,000
How about it, Silver
Blade? If you insist on

372
00:21:15,083 --> 00:21:19,583
staying in the Special Zone,
why not join our proud Coven?

373
00:21:19,666 --> 00:21:23,375
We'd certainly welcome you,
if you were one of us.

374
00:21:23,458 --> 00:21:25,083
I've heard enough.

375
00:21:26,041 --> 00:21:27,541
Kotaro.

376
00:21:30,041 --> 00:21:31,458
What are you doing, Jiro?

377
00:21:31,541 --> 00:21:33,750
You launched this
sneak attack on us.

378
00:21:33,833 --> 00:21:36,125
And you've treated
us with such rudeness.

379
00:21:36,208 --> 00:21:40,083
And now you ask, at gunpoint
no less, that I join you.

380
00:21:40,166 --> 00:21:43,625
Your stupidity and ignorance
will lead you to your demise.

381
00:21:43,708 --> 00:21:45,833
At my own hands.

382
00:21:45,916 --> 00:21:47,541
I'll mete out your punishment.

383
00:21:47,625 --> 00:21:50,416
After that, maybe
you'll finally wise up.

384
00:22:15,458 --> 00:22:16,500
Die!

385
00:23:59,791 --> 00:24:03,000
Did you say your name
was Kotaro? To be honest,

386
00:24:03,083 --> 00:24:07,125
I've developed quite an interest
